      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <div class="icon">📊</div>
        <h3>Analytics & Insights</h3>
        <p>Advanced analytics to track lecturer performance and institute engagement for better decision-making.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <div class="icon">🤖</div>
        <h3>AI Recommendations</h3>
        <p>AI-powered suggestions for matching lecturers with institutes based on needs and expertise.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <div class="icon">🎥</div>
        <h3>Live Online Sessions</h3>
        <p>Integration of live video sessions for remote lectures, workshops, and collaborative projects.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

